description.en: KNUCKLES is an ERC-20 token aimed to build a strong, game-based community. KNUCKLES was launched as part of the $TAILS ecosystem. BOTH tokens will be marketed together. Gaming, NFT, and staking will be available for the ecosystem itself. HODL both TAILS and KNUCKLES for rewards. Part of our tokenomics helps to increase our liquidity by adding part of sell transactions to LP!
